    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_27.png[/img]While along the roads, your wardogs suddenly scamper off and begin digging into the earth. You're not sure why as you don't recall giving either one a bone. A few moments later and they're fighting over what appears to be %finding%. You interrupt the tug of war, taking the goods for yourself. The hounds whine, but a few good pets settles them down.",
